{"tid":1684886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《獨立調查特首違法或瀆職行為議案》投票 - 香港全民議政會","createTime":"2019-10-31T10:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T13:48:44.000Z","uid":300718,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b2df8e8750b7a49736b4927407589d3b605047da","tid":1684886,"uid":300718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">投票及公佈Channel： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=ea2deac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n公海： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkassembly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkassembly&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=ebe6fecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkassembly</a><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n- - - - - <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「香港全民議政會」有關《獨立調查特首違法或瀆職行為議案》投票（31 Oct - 2 Nov）</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【議員議案：由25名議員聯合動議（楊岳橋議員為動議人）】<br />\n根據《基本法》第七十三條第（九）項動議的議案：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">立法會25名議員聯合動議，以組成獨立調查委員會，指控行政長官林鄭月娥有嚴重違法及／或瀆職行為。</span><br />\n<br />\n《獨立調查特首違法或瀆職行為議案》（及其附表）和背景資料：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">立法會25名議員聯合動議，以組成獨立調查委員會，指控行政長官林鄭月娥有嚴重違法及／或瀆職行為。指控內容主要包括：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 無視主流民意反對，強推備受爭議的法案<br />\n2. 採用過份武力鎮壓和平集會<br />\n3. 以不合比例的控罪打壓示威者<br />\n4. 造成社會撕裂</span><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n1. 《獨立調查特首違法或瀆職行為議案》及其附表：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/legco-20191029-1-1-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Flegco-20191029-1-1-c&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=166ef12a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/legco-20191029-1-1-c</a><br />\n2. 《基本法》第七十三條第（九）項：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/BasicLaw-chapter4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FBasicLaw-chapter4&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=79e4245a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/BasicLaw-chapter4</a><br />\n<br />\n- - - - - <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">投票及公佈Channel： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=ea2deac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n公海： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkassembly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkassembly&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=ebe6fecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkassembly</a><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n- - - - - <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">《動議譴責何君堯議員的議案》投票結果</span><br />\n<br />\n於10月15日，立法會內務委員會選舉主席。期間，何君堯指毛孟靜「食慣洋腸」。主持會議的公民黨郭榮鏗指，因何君堯使用的詞語與性別及性器官有關，言辭具冒犯性，所以要求他馬上收回及道歉。然而，何君堯以「言論自由」為由拒絕，郭榮鏗續宣佈驅逐何君堯離場。何君堯最後自行離開會議廳。<br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜議員隨後根據《議事規則》第49B(1A)條提出動議譴責何君堯議員的議案。該議案由朱凱廸議員、陳志全議員及范國威議員聯名簽署。<br />\n<br />\n我們隨即就議案進行投票，以下是投票結果。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">《動議譴責何君堯議員的議案》（5193個投票）</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>* 98% 贊成<br />\n* 1% 反對<br />\n* 1% 棄權/無意見</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n備註：此議案已被列於今天（31/10/2019）的立法會會議議程。<br />\n<br />\n- - - - -<br />\n投票： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkvote/89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote%2F89&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=a04f378c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkvote/89</a><br />\n背景資料： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkvote/88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote%2F88&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=2f17189f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkvote/88</a><br />\n上次投票結果： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkvote/87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote%2F87&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=949ab47a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkvote/87</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港全民議政會</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">※全民議政，以民制權※</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>投票及公佈Channel： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkvote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkvote&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=ea2deac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkvote</a><br />\n議政廳： <a href=\"http://t.me/hkassembly\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkassembly&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnA9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=ebe6fecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkassembly</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ad6b26c6231d62179c43d88b10420c22480f5971","tid":1684886,"uid":281252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:17:03.000Z","msg":"P牌推推"},{"pid":"677573120306f3812a659a1ee34d476a666ea568","tid":1684886,"uid":37802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:19:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfeb72d103f5a732e91373c3630afac131712098","tid":1684886,"uid":220045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"fddb7afd297da9d73c9b98ef82164d4ff33caea5","tid":1684886,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaf8130c6215166e8839d6120e4ea7ebf5cf4770","tid":1684886,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42c06baeb22b6cae9b52d684deda8c802ca179f","tid":1684886,"uid":102529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:08:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e6e62b636f45793b2592f9d3005d91b30da9a05","tid":1684886,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"試下每個留言加入新中國社會主義下既偉大產物，&ldquo;甴近平&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg